OL,5, The Post Office continued to threaten  
OL,6, two sisters over a #34,000 shortfall   
OL,7, even after a criminal trial was ruled  
OL,8, out over faulty computer evidence, BBC 
OL,9, Scotland has learned.                  
OL,11,FA Glasgow prosecutor rejected the case 
OL,12,Fin 2014 because of "issues" with the   
OL,13,FHorizon computer system.               
OL,15,FHowever, the Post Office did not tell  
OL,16,FJacquie El Kasaby and Rose Stewart the 
OL,17,Freason for the failed prosecution.     
OL,19,FInstead they threatened to involve debt
OL,20,Fcollectors if they did not pay.        
